		//explode flare11 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | FIRE | SMOKE | FALL | NOHEATCLOUD;
		//explode flare12 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | FIRE | SMOKE | FALL | NOHEATCLOUD;
		//explode flare13 type EXPLODE_ON_HIT | FIRE | SMOKE | FALL | NOHEATCLOUD;
